# BOOK VI

### HYMN I

#### In praise of Savitar

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0600101">1</span></span>Sing,
Atharvana, at eve, sing loudly, bring a splendid present:  
   hymn God Savitar with praises.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0600102">2</span></span>Yea, praise
him whose home is in the river, Son of Truth, the  
   youthful, gracious friend whose word is guileless.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0600103">3</span></span>Savitar our
God shall send us many everlasting treasures, that  
   both paths may well be travelled.

